      "parameters": {
        "color": 7,
        "width": 440,
        "height": 600,
        "content": "## Whitelist\n\nThis block will activate if the Bot_Whitelist_Active parameter in the Settings node is set to true and Allowed_Chat_IDs is specified (comma-separated, e.g., \"1234, 4567\")."
